DISCOVER HAWAII!
EASIER THAN EVER WITH UNITED!
Hawaii! Tropical dreamland of radiant flowers, graceful
palm trees, warm, sapphire-hued waters. Glorious land of
high volcanic mountains, fields
of sugar cane, rows of
stubby pineapples, wipe-outs, surfies and the hula.
And United
can take
you there any day you choose.
Leave in the morning and start your suntan that afternoon
on the beach at Waikiki. Choose from three classes of serv-
ice. And the fare from San Francisco is as low as $100.
And charge your entire trip with United's Personal Travel
Credit Card.
Call your Travel Agent or us.
Aloha!
